>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>20</td>\n<td><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://static-images.vnncdn.net/files/publish/2022/9/19/da-bai-atletico-real-madrid-doi-lai-ngoi-dau-tu-tay-barca-6508cbfc9ed94a5cb047c6d6f016dc63.png\">Elche</a></td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>-14</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<article class=\"ck-cms-wiki-news-full vnn-template-noneditable\"><a href=\"/ket-qua-bong-da-lyon-0-1-psg-vong-8-ligue-1-2061433.html\" class=\"summary__image\"><img src=\"https://static-images.vnncdn.net/files/publish/2022/9/19/lyon-psg-12-but-joie-messi-48.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n<div class=\"summary__content\"><a class=\"summary__content-title\" href=\"/ket-qua-bong-da-lyon-0-1-psg-vong-8-ligue-1-2061433.html\">Messi ghi tuyệt phẩm, PSG chễm chệ đỉnh bảng</a><span class=\"summary__content-desc\">Lionel Messi bàn duy nhất giúp PSG đánh bại Lyon ở vòng 8 Ligue 1, qua đó đòi lại ngôi đầu từ tay Marseille.</span></div>\n</article>\n                            </div>"}